@DATABASE "Cannonball"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - C - Cannonball"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - C
                   ====================================

                                Cannonball
                                ==========


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(32957,0)"}          32957,0
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(32807,255)"}          32807,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         I haven't tested this one as I don't have the
                         game :(

                         Rastan
@endnode
